    <obo:IAO_0000115>A serine/threonine protein kinase complex involved in cell survival, apoptosis and autophagic cell death pathways. DAPK1 is activated by the dephosphorylation of a n-terminal serine and calcium-calmodulin binding.</obo:IAO_0000115>
    <oboInOwl:created_by>bhm</oboInOwl:created_by>
    <oboInOwl:creation_date>2015-04-01T13:05:17Z</oboInOwl:creation_date>
