    <oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>AICD</oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>
    <oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>activated T cell apoptosis</oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>
    <oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>antigen-driven apoptosis</oboInOwl:hasBroadSynonym>
