    <owl:annotatedTarget>down-regulation of neuron intrinsic apoptotic signaling pathway in response to endoplasmic reticulum stress</owl:annotatedTarget>
    <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>GOC:TermGenie</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
